data.description: Showing start Friday 9/29 on this fully renovated two bed, two bath, open concept 2 story located in the rapidly appreciating Woodland Park neighborhood. This home features laminate floors throughout the first floor, white cabinets, butcher block countertops, a knock off the kitchen that would make a great future half bath. The glass door of the dining room leads to a deck overlooking the oversized, fenced rear yard. There is a one and a half car block garage, and parking for two additional cars in the rear. The second floor primary suite offers a shower bath and abundant closet space. There is also a large second bedroom with several closets and a full tub bath off the hall. The sellers have made many improvements since their purchase and are only moving because of a job relocation.
